146
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:37,990
You serious?

147
00:08:37,990 --> 00:08:39,030
I am.

148
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,050
Do you have any problem?

149
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,090
