181
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:43,030
Top.

182
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:46,120
Top.

183
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,280
Top.

184
00:10:55,180 --> 00:10:55,890
Top.

185
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,410
Top.

186
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,930
I had the gut to ask you

187
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,550
because I knew you share the feelings too.

188
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,050
Top.

189
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,810
Honestly, I was embarrassed that night

190
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,690
