193
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,970
I just did what I wanted.

194
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:49,870
What if I told you that I agreed just because

195
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,290
I wanted to save your face?

196
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:03,630
You may think you’re hot, rich,

197
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,880
and get whatever you want.

198
00:12:06,730 --> 00:12:10,190
But honestly, you’re not entirely my type.

199
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:16,020
What’s your type then?

200
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,560
Many traits.

201
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:22,000
I don’t know if you will tick all my checklist boxes.

202
00:12:24,570 --> 00:12:25,490
Just tell me.

203
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,920
I’m sure I tick all of it.

204
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:30,840
Look at you being so confident.

205
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,890
I am.

206
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:36,580
