217
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,940
He must love my friends

218
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:57,310
and get along with them.

219
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:00,670
Most importantly, he must not keep secrets from me.

220
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:02,700
He must not lie to me.

221
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,490
That’s it.

222
00:14:43,530 --> 00:14:45,710
Running your business inside university walls

223
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:49,470
