253
00:16:52,290 --> 00:16:54,470
No, I’m just here to chill out.

254
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,050
Your first time here?

255
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:57,730
It is.

256
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:01,800
I really like newcomers.

257
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,360
Let me take care of you tonight.

258
00:17:04,610 --> 00:17:06,610
