276
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,230
You’re really something.

277
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,600
Who are you?

278
00:18:12,170 --> 00:18:13,560
Pablo Escobar?

279
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:17,500
Whatever shit I’m selling is my business.

